---
import IndexLayout from "../layouts/indexLayout.astro";
---

<IndexLayout languague="en">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50 py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
      <div class="px-6 py-8 md:p-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-center text-gray-900 mb-8">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8 text-right">
          Effective date: {new Date().toLocaleDateString("en-US", { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Introduction</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Welcome to IberiaEye, your essential road assistant for Spanish roads. 
              We are committed to protecting your privacy and handling your data in a 
              transparent and responsible manner. This Privacy Policy details how we 
              treat your information and what your rights are regarding it.
            </p>
          </section>
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Data We Collect and Permissions Used</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-3">
              To improve user experience and provide key features, 
              IberiaEye requires and may use the following permissions and data:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li class="leading-relaxed">
                <span class="font-semibold">Internet access and network state (INTERNET, ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE):</span> 
                Necessary to obtain real-time information about traffic, 
                road conditions, and app updates.
              </li>
              <li class="leading-relaxed">
                <span class="font-semibold">Precise and approximate location (ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION, ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION):</span> 
                Allows us to locate your exact position to provide relevant information 
                about your immediate road environment.
              </li>
              <li class="leading-relaxed">
                <span class="font-semibold">Background location (ACCESS_BACKGROUND_LOCATION):</span> 
                The application can access your location even when not actively in use, 
                to provide real-time alerts about traffic conditions, 
                road hazards, and personalized updates.
              </li>
              <li class="leading-relaxed">
                <span class="font-semibold">Notifications (POST_NOTIFICATIONS):</span> 
                Allows sending important alerts and relevant updates to your device.
              </li>
              <li class="leading-relaxed">
                <span class="font-semibold">Foreground service (FOREGROUND_SERVICE, FOREGROUND_SERVICE_LOCATION):</span> 
                Allows the application to run essential processes while minimized, 
                such as continuous location monitoring for traffic alerts.
              </li>
              <li class="leading-relaxed">
                <span class="font-semibold">Usage analytics:</span> 
                We use Firebase to collect anonymous data about app performance 
                and improve the user experience.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Use of Information</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-3">
              The collected data is used to:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li class="leading-relaxed">
                Display real-time information about traffic and road conditions.
              </li>
              <li class="leading-relaxed">
                Improve app functionality and performance.
              </li>
              <li class="leading-relaxed">
                Ensure a personalized and efficient user experience.
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mt-3 font-semibold">
              IberiaEye does not sell, share, or use data for advertising purposes.
            </p>
          </section>
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Prominent Disclosure and Consent</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-3">
              <span class="font-semibold">Background Location Usage:</span> 
              Before accessing background location, IberiaEye will display 
              a clear and explicit notice within the app, explaining the 
              reason for the request. Location will only be collected if the user 
              expressly grants permission.
            </p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Additionally, users can manage location permissions at any time 
              from their device settings.
            </p>
          </section>
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Data Security</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              We take security seriously and apply appropriate measures to 
              protect collected data against unauthorized access, alterations, 
              or disclosures.
            </p>
          </section>
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">User Rights</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-3">
              As a user, you have the following rights:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li class="leading-relaxed">
                Access, correct, or delete collected data.
              </li>
              <li class="leading-relaxed">
                Revoke location permission at any time from device settings.
              </li>
              <li class="leading-relaxed">
                Contact us if you have privacy concerns.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Changes to the Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally to reflect 
              changes in our application or for other operational, legal, or 
              regulatory reasons. If we make changes, we will notify you through an 
              application update or other appropriate means.
            </p>
          </section>
          
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Contact</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, 
              please don't hesitate to contact us at 
              <a href="mailto:contact@marcoscuesta.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">
                contact@marcoscuesta.com
              </a>.
            </p>
          </section>
          
          <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-6 mt-6">
            <p class="font-bold text-center text-gray-900">
              Thank you for trusting IberiaEye and allowing us to be your eyes on the road.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</IndexLayout>